{"tid":235402,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴絲身邊既人會夢遊","createTime":"2017-05-09T03:48:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T06:30:14.000Z","uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4db6877c1bc065307e084339b38b7de17c5c42","tid":235402,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:48:56.000Z","msg":"呢排有個朋友，做做下野都會恰著同夢遊，好得人驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢話自己平時唔會咁，係呢排唔開心先會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實知佢呢排壓力好大，感情又有問題，上網睇過夢遊同抑鬱症可能有關係，我覺得佢都似係呢個情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我應該點幫佢，係咪應該帶佢睇精神科？"},{"pid":"0b667be3d51e8c63f99808fdac3147226e8c28e4","tid":235402,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:53:34.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好沉得咁快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819cbbd8b1cd6ccb7c0b2dec4cda3fb365f03144","tid":235402,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:58:46.000Z","msg":"推推，真係好擔心佢"},{"pid":"bbe65e4942e208f4282b4e47ef8b762289ba34a4","tid":235402,"uid":18279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:34:40.000Z","msg":"上連登搵醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9fbbd42457e5979e4706d85689da6d5466da29f","tid":235402,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T05:00:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上連登搵醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁身邊無醫生同第一次見到人夢遊咪睇下有無人有相似經歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad97a2c47d7e4e8da240f33f6c6491d275b146d","tid":235402,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T06:30:14.000Z","msg":"乜原來咁少人會夢遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}